Class DoubleDataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.DoubleDataSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSet

    public final class DoubleDataSet
extends Object
implements DataSet
    A collection of numerical observations represented as primitive doubles. This class is immutable and thread-safe.
